6/29/83 forum request:  previous, prev

Syntax: prev {trans_spec} {-control_args}


Syntax as an active request:  [prev {trans_spec} {-control_args}]


Function:
Prints or returns the transaction index of the transaction before the
specified transaction, or before the current transaction if no
trans_spec is given.


Arguments:
trans_spec
   is the transaction for which the previous transaction is desired.


Control arguments:
-include_deleted, -idl
   print or return the index of the previous transaction even if it is 
   deleted.
-only_deleted, -odl
   print or return the index of the previous deleted transaction.
-only_non_deleted, -ondl
   print or return the index of the previous non-deleted transaction.
   (Default)
